line_1: His coat of darkness on his loins he braced;
line_2: His shoes of swiftness on his feet he placed;

line_1: With nervous Cords their Hands are firmly brac'd;
line_2: Their round black Eye-balls in their Bosom plac'd;

line_1: So may thy languid limbs with strength be brac'd,
line_2: With fair renown thy public virtue grac'd,

line_1: Her spear yet lifted, and her corslet brac'd,
line_2: Thy wond'rous tale, and cheer the list'ning waste.

line_1: Her Robe (which closely by the Girdle brac't
line_2: Reveal'd the Beauties of a slender Waste)
